<para>
  Mean thresholding converts all pixels brighter than the mean
  brightness of an &image; <varname>value</varname> to white and all
  pixels darker than it to black. 
</para>
<para>
   The &image; is first converted from color to grayscale if
   necessary.
</para>
<para>
  <classname>MeanThreshold</classname> is a wrapper around the
  &skimage; routine <ulink
  url="https://scikit-image.org/docs/stable/api/skimage.filters.html#skimage.filters.threshold_mean"><code>skimage.filters.threshold_mean</code></ulink>.
</para>
  

<figure id="Figure-Threshold-Mean">
